SUMMARY:How to really connect and find love
DESCRIPTION:Try New Things in Toronto!\nIt’s not too late!!! You could c
 hange your whole social life in the course of a few weeks if you take the 
 right steps…\n\nThere is one thing you can focus on that will increase y
 our results in pretty much every single area of your life: becoming more s
 ocially confident. **It’s the most important thing for your longevity\, 
 your sense of well being\, your career success\, your happiness quotient.*
 *\n\nAcross the board\, your ability to connect with others is your BIGGES
 T advantage in life.\n\nCome check out our free workshop to help you get t
 o know **where to meet like minded people in the real world**\, exactly wh
 at you should say and **how to keep the conversation going once you get it
  started.**\n\nMy name is Devon O’Brien Ash and I’ve been teaching thi
 s stuff for 18 years through my company[ www.socialfluency.com](http://www
 .socialfluency.com). I’ve worked with tens of thousands of people so you
  know the things\nI am going to be sharing are reality tested and proven t
 o work!\n\nI’m not just going to be regurgitating something I read somew
 here… This is the real deal!\n\nCome join us and learn the art and scien
 ce of powerful communication.
