 t of all it's a lot of fun)\n\n\\*Joined by my other groups too so we can 
 anticipate a fabulous day :)\n\n**Where to Meet us?**\n\n**Date: Sunday Ap
 ril 12th**\n**Arrive between 4:00 pm - 4:30 pm**\n**Location:** La Carnita
  - Good Fortune Bar (Main Floor)\n**Address:** 130 Eglinton Ave. Toronto\,
  ON M4P 2X9\n\nEvent Details Below:\n\nSincerely\,\n\nSteve Flemming\n(Mus
 ic Bingo Host)\n\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\
 -\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\n**Details of Event:**\n\n**\\*MU
 SIC BINGO\\***\n**(An Afternoon of Fun\, Treats and Great Music!)**\n\n-Lo
 ts of laughs and thrills in store as we enjoy a terrific afternoon making 
