 d in a super fun designed format :)\n\n\\*Treats handed out to the winning
  participants during each round we play\n\n\\*Invite your friends or come 
 on your own!\n\n**Event Fee:**\n10 dollars at the door (cash only please)\
 nIncludes: **Music Bingo\,** treats\, reserved room/seating\, lots of laug
 hs and plenty of fun people to play the game with)\n\\*or e-transfer in ad
